'Jones' is an unincorporated place in Unorganized Kenora District in
northwestern Ontario, Canada.

It lies on the Canadian National Railway transcontinental main line, between Farlane to the west and Favel to the east,
and is passed but not served by Via Rail transcontinental [[Canadian
(train)|Canadian]] trains. Jones is also on Ontario Highway 671, which heads
southwest to city of Kenora.
